{"TopicId":165763,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"How do you texture your planets?","CreatedByName":"EricL","CreatedById":169181,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-23T13:22:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"EricL","CreatedById":169181,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-23T13:22:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi everyone,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs I continue developing my mod Intergalactic, I\u0027m starting to wonder... what\u0027s the best method of texturing a planet? Procedural? SpaceEngine? Or simply drawing it from scratch on programs like Gimp? I\u0027m just asking for your opinion on how I should go about doing this.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Poodmund","CreatedById":128643,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-23T15:04:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMany different ways, some like to hand paint/stitch their together, some like to procedurally create terrain maps and others use programs like Space Engine to do it all for them. I created a thread recently with a lot of resources on Planet Texture Mapping:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed1200881904\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/165285-planetary-texturing-guide-repository/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is also a Discord server hosted by Gameslinx where members discuss planet making:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://discord.gg/akSFm4v\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#4588c5;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00229T3uf2Z.png\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/9T3uf2Z.png\u0022 style=\u0022border-style:none;vertical-align:middle;\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-09-23T15:24:47Z\u0022 title=\u002209/23/2017 03:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 23, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Poodmund\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SamBelanger","CreatedById":166917,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-23T18:43:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EYou can ask me that I make you textures \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}